%livy2.spark

val df_hvbp3 = df_hvbp2.withColumn(
    "Performance_Rating",
    when(
        $"Performance_Rating".equalTo("Not Available") || $"Performance_Rating".equalTo("NaN") || $"Performance_Rating".equalTo(" ") || $"Performance_Rating".equalTo("69.01") || $"Performance_Rating".equalTo("65.23") || $"Performance_Rating".equalTo("85.79"),
        null
        ).otherwise($"Performance_Rating")).withColumn(
    "Improvement_Points",
    when(
        $"Improvement_Points".equalTo("Not Available") || $"Improvement_Points".equalTo(" "),
        null
        ).otherwise($"Improvement_Points")).withColumn(
    "Improvement_Points",
    when(
        $"Improvement_Points".equalTo("9 out of 10") || $"Improvement_Points".equalTo("10 out of 10"),
        "9 out of 9"
        ).otherwise($"Improvement_Points"))
        
df_hvbp3.printSchema()
df_hvbp3.show(50)

val dropDuplicates = renameColunas.distinct()

dropDuplicates.count()
dropDuplicates.printSchema()
dropDuplicates.show(1000)
